{"tid":2415060,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"許樹昌：若短時間大部分市民接種疫苗或可放寬防疫措施","createTime":"2021-02-20T03:05:01.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-20T03:43:33.000Z","uid":350584,"like":1,"dislike":13,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"ba8fc95f6d71b2ea78292f039fa1e349bf79953c","tid":2415060,"uid":350584,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-20T03:05:01.000Z","msg":"【Now新聞台】政府專家顧問許樹昌認為，如果大部分市民在短時間內接種新冠病毒疫苗，或可以逐步放寬防疫措施。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.now.com/mobile/local/player?newsId=424688\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fmobile%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D424688&d=8a%2F9oMJQTUqWgqWpHd%2BbktRt30ToQ9uN2xIpFOlVN1U%3D&h=1218d054\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fmobile%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D424688&h=88b6268c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/mobile/local/player?newsId=424688</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3a9d9001d3a86b7bb1d4735c4c046d0c838a4dbd","tid":2415060,"uid":350584,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-20T03:05:40.000Z","msg":"許樹昌：「視乎公眾參與接種疫苗的比例，如果大部分社區人士很短時間參與接種疫苗、有抗體，措施相信可以逐漸放鬆。不過戴口罩、洗手等習慣相信要維持一段長時間，因為第一代疫苗是減低有徵狀感染，不是完全無事。」<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"58d971b3edbb21310769b4fc44adb9f400ab6172","tid":2415060,"uid":350584,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-20T03:06:47.000Z","msg":"因為第一代疫苗是減低有徵狀感染，不是完全無事。"},{"pid":"f30464ce321c9d8decad7f208f3034b37209e549","tid":2415060,"uid":350584,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-20T03:10:25.000Z","msg":"許樹昌在節目後表示，一般來說，如有7成以上市民接種疫苗並產生抗體，便會有群體保護效應，社區確診個案自然會減少，期望年底或之前可以做到。但他強調，打針是中長期措施，其他的社交距離措施亦有助遏止疫情，甚至「清零」，因此不等於要等待數個月後，有7成市民打針後才可放寬整體防疫措施"},{"pid":"dc1197616196499c8143ebe9f84e2b9862323d9e","tid":2415060,"uid":8170,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-20T03:11:15.000Z","msg":"之前話群體免疫要 70% 人有抗體<br />\n但疫苗呢，就得 50% 效果<br />\n咁要做到 70% 人有抗體，接種人數要去到 140%，即香港要有 750萬 x 140% = 1050萬人打咗針先有效。 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f03add39c7aecf7efa69636980468b20c576685d","tid":2415060,"uid":198822,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-20T03:11:40.000Z","msg":"問你打唔打又含糊其詞，含撚啦社會賢達<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bb98c1ec5e3b5351bd6fcb3552b24648a5645bea","tid":2415060,"uid":149925,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-20T03:31:09.000Z","msg":"唔會打"},{"pid":"0d42e887254ebf01af1a00158b4f0f3919263fec","tid":2415060,"uid":174246,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-20T03:33:19.000Z","msg":"愈多人打，就早d同中國通關，放多d中國人落嚟，咁大家自己決定lu<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b32da9b7602ae1e8413e3da7c10a7eee1ab44acb","tid":2415060,"uid":106,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0d42e887254ebf01af1a00158b4f0f3919263fec","tid":2415060,"uid":174246,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-20T03:33:19.000Z","msg":"愈多人打，就早d同中國通關，放多d中國人落嚟，咁大家自己決定lu<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-20T03:34:29.000Z","msg":"不過班中國人就唔洗打針<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"538e026f84fe9d5b489cea3813ce8657a70b89df","tid":2415060,"u